cu.explanation_en: Setting the AMF IP address to an unreachable subnet '10.0.0.1' will cause routing failures, preventing the DU from establishing connection to the AMF and leading to F1 setup rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the SSB absolute frequency to 0 (invalid value) will cause frequency misalignment, resulting in SSB transmission failure and cell synchronization issues.
du.explanation_zh: 將 SSB 絕對頻率設定為 0（無效值）會導致頻率錯位，造成 SSB 傳輸失敗和細胞同步問題。
